{"tid":1974331,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"<黃色經濟圈>番茄師兄登陸元朗 逆市開新店！","createTime":"2020-04-15T18:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T18:20:48.000Z","uid":227801,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c23f5df3ace1e576ebc09bbfceaac34ad46d1de0","tid":1974331,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T18:38:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/1030240/dining/番茄師兄-元朗-深水埗/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F1030240%2Fdining%2F%E7%95%AA%E8%8C%84%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%84-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=c0c401de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/1030240/dining/番茄師兄-元朗-深水埗/</a><br />\n<br />\n主打番茄湯麵的深水埗小店「番茄師兄」近日登陸元朗啦！小店能在疫情之下逆市開店，除了老闆夠人情味街坊最like之餘，當然少不了招牌鮮甜番茄湯和軟腍牛腩！<br />\n<br />\n番茄師兄元朗逆市開分店！<br />\n<br />\n深水埗小店番茄師兄近日於元朗擊壤路開設分店，負責人在Facebook專頁分享喜訊，不過亦提到新店開業不久，出品和上菜時間仍有進步空間，望食客見諒。不過記者在元朗飲食Facebook群組看到街坊拍攝到餐廳門前人龍盛況，相信大家都會力撐番茄師兄！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/92927541_2530186190575748_2644562757449416704_n_14656299475e96ccfece740.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F92927541_2530186190575748_2644562757449416704_n_14656299475e96ccfece740.jpg&h=916c2f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/93305479_3665633640174565_3524319050630955008_n_212605945e96cd5652cfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F93305479_3665633640174565_3524319050630955008_n_212605945e96cd5652cfd.jpg&h=b6b88542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n番茄師兄（元朗店）<br />\n<br />\n地址：元朗擊壤路9號金寶大廈地下4號舖（顯示地圖）<br />\n電話：3615 1062<br />\n營業時間：12:30pm-9pm（試業期間不固定，詳情可到Facebook專頁查看）"},{"pid":"dce0a9461fae34a8353cdbedc6a3fac494a644ef","tid":1974331,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":